      "content": "i don't think i can do this anymore. everything i worked for for the last 5 years... the lab results, the funding, the dissertation... it's all just gone. i wake up and the weight of it just feels physical. i'm so tired of fighting for a life that doesn't even feel like mine anymore. i just want everything to stop. i just want peace.",
